# Design System

- **Colors**: Zinc gray base, TRAC Blue (#0c0563) primary, use CSS variables
- **Font**: Rajdhani
- **Typography**: Section `text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground`, label `text-xs text-muted-foreground`, value `font-medium`
- **Radius**: `rounded-md`/`rounded-lg`, badges `rounded-full`
- **Shadows**: Minimal, prefer borders
